des:
WOOX Security products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your smart devices.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your smart devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.After connecting Alexa to your WOOX Security products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "WOOX Security" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "WOOX Security" app;
(3). You need to have some WOOX Security devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "WOOX Security" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "WOOX Security" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "WOOX Security" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "WOOX Security", and you'll be navigated to "WOOX Security" login page;
(9). Input your WOOX Security account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
